                            "type": "line",
                            "description": "Total S(IV) oxidation rate R_FeMn as a function of dissolved Mn(II). At low Mn(II) the rate is set by the Mn-independent Fe-only term; as Mn(II) rises the synergistic term takes over and R_FeMn climbs.",
                            "x": {
                                "variable": "Mn_II",
                                "label": "dissolved Mn(II) concentration (mol/m^3)"
                            },
                            "y": {
